            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>格羅方德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GFS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GFS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GFS-US</a>)截至台北時間04日21:36股價上漲1.85美元，報38.72美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量221,713（股），盤中最高價38.75美元、最低價37.10美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.19%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.33%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.42%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.27%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>格羅方德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GFS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GFS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GFS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-3.31%</li> <li>近 1 月：-1.32%</li> <li>近 3 月：-2.6%</li> <li>近 6 月：-19.52%</li> <li>今年以來：-16.29%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6007295",
